{"title_page": "YoungBoy Never Broke Again discography", "text_new": "{{Infobox artist discography\n| Artist          = [[YoungBoy Never Broke Again]]\n| Image           = NBA YOUNGBOY 2018.png\n| Caption         = Gaulden in 2018\n| Alt             = \n| Studio          = 8\n| Live            = \n| Compilation     = 1\n| Video           = \n| Option name     = Mixtapes\n| Option          = 14\n| Music videos    =\n| EP              = 3\n| Singles         = 27\n}}\nThe discography of American rapper [[YoungBoy Never Broke Again]] (also known as NBA YoungBoy) consists of 1 [[studio album]], 1 [[compilation album]], 14 [[mixtape]]s, 2 collaborative mixtapes, 3 [[extended play]]s, 9 [[Single (music)|singles]] (including 2 as a featured artist) and 2 [[promotional single]]s.\n\n==Albums==\n===Studio album===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ Studio album with selected details\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:13em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em\"| [[List of music recording certifications |Certifications]]\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br/><ref name=\"BB200\" />\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums|US<br/>R&B/HH]]<br/><ref name=RBHHA />\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Canadian Albums Chart|CAN]]<br/><ref name=\"CANA\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/music/youngboy-never-broke-again/chart-history/CNA|title=YoungBoy Never Broke Again \u2013 Chart history (Canadian Albums)|work=Billboard|accessdate=March 3, 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Until Death Call My Name]]''\n|\n* Released: April 27, 2018 <small>(US)</small>\n* Label: Never Broke Again, [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]]\n* Format: Digital download\n| 7 || 5 || 38 \n|\n* [[Recording Industry Associ