hive.org/web/20061004064138/http://www.stjohns.k12.fl.us/about/press/050206.html |archive-date= October 4, 2006 |url-status= dead |df= mdy-all }}</ref> || 2002\u20132003 || 2005\u20132006 || 4 years\n|-\n| Brennan Asplen<ref name=Principal2 /> || 2006\u20132007 || 2010\u20132011 || 5 years\n|-\n| Dawn Sapp<ref name=Principal3>{{cite web |url= http://www-mms.stjohns.k12.fl.us/parents/Administrative%20Changes%205-5-11.pdf |title= Media release: May 5, 2011 - New Principal at Bartram Trail HS |accessdate= 2011-03-09 |date= May 8, 2011 |publisher= St. Johns County School District |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331084616/http://www-mms.stjohns.k12.fl.us/parents/Administrative%20Changes%205-5-11.pdf |archivedate=2012-03-31 }}</ref> || 2011\u20132012 || 2014-2015 || 4 years\n|-\n|Chris Phelps || 2015-2016 || present || \n|-\n|}\n\n==Demographics==\nBartram Trail's [[education|enrollment]] trends show enrollment increases with each year.\n<center>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"margin: 1em auto 1em auto\"\n|+ \n! 2000-01 || 2001-02 || 2002-03 || 2003-04 || 2004-05 || 2005-06 || 2006-07 || 2007-08\n|-\n| 1,246 <ref name=Digger /> || 1,529 <ref name=FTU092507 /> || 1,840 <ref name=Digger /> || 2,124 <ref name=Digger /> || 2,281 <ref name=Digger /> || 2,486 <ref name=Digger /> || 2,615 <ref name=Digger /> || 2,627 <ref name=FTU082901 />\n|}\n</center>\n\nThe [[ethnic group|ethnicity]] of Bartram Trail's students is as follows (last updated for the 2006-2007 school year):\n\n<center>\n{| class=\"sortable wikitable\" style=\"margin: 1em auto 1em auto\"\n|+ \n! Ethnicity:|| School <ref name=PDFBT /><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.greatschools.net/cgi-bin/fl/other/5120#students |title= \"Bartram Trail High School: Student Ethnicity\" on greatschools.net |accessdate= 2008-03-09 |year= 2007| archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080331211009/http://www.greatschools.net/cgi-bin/fl/other/5120| archivedate= 31 March 2008 | url-status= live}}</ref><br>Percentage: || 