thor=Full Circle Literary |year=2017 |title=David Bowles |url=http://www.fullcircleliterary.com/david-bowles/ |work=Middle Grade & Young Adult |publisher=Full Circle Literary |accessdate=2017-06-18 |ref={{sfnref|Full Circle}} }} \n* {{cite web |author=Michael David Wilson |year=2017 |title=TIH 132: David Bowles on Mexican-American Folklore, Southern Gothic, and Story Ideas |url=http://www.thisishorror.co.uk/tih-132-david-bowles-on-mexican-american-folklore-southern-gothic-and-story-ideas/ |work=This Is Horror Podcast |publisher=This Is Horror |accessdate=2017-07-01 |ref={{sfnref|This Is Horror}} }}\n* {{cite web |author=Nicole Brinkley |year=2017 |title=What authors received YA book deals in February? |url=http://www.yainterrobang.com/ya-book-deals-february-2017/ |work=YA Interrobang |publisher=YA Interrobang |accessdate=2018-05-08 |ref={{sfnref|Book Deals}} }}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|David Bowles}}\n* {{Official website}}\n* {{IMDb name|nm5912074}}\n* [https://www.worldcat.org/identities/np-bowles,%20David/ David Bowles] at [[WorldCat]] \u2013 multiple people with this name <!-- 2016-02-09 Bowles is not yet identified in LC Catalog (no LCCN) -->\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Bowles, David}}\n[[Category:Poets from Texas]]\n[[Category:American poets of Mexican descent]]\n[[Category:Hispanic and Latino American poets]]\n[[Category:Mestizo writers]]\n[[Category:21st-century American poets]]\n[[Category:21st-century translators]]\n[[Category:University of Texas\u2013Pan American people]]\n[[Category:People from Upper Marlboro, Maryland]]\n[[Category:University of Texas\u2013Pan American alumni]]\n[[Category:1970 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Donna, Texas]]\n[[Category:Spanish\u2013English translators]]\n[[Category:Japanese\u2013English translators]]\n[[Category:Translators from Nahuatl]]\n[[Category:Translators from Mayan]]\n[[Category:21st-century American male writers]]\n[[Category:American male poets]]\n", 